### Enforcement
Our goal is education and a healthy space — not “gotcha” moderation. But we will act to protect the community.

Enforcement actions and major decisions may be summarized in <#1136343213091856486> for transparency and comment.

General Mod Actions(mods may escalate to these steps at their discretion):

**Reminder / Warning**– A ping or DM pointing to the relevant guideline.

**Short Timeout** – Temporary mute if behavior continues.

**Longer Timeout & Review** – Longer mute and discussion among Stewards/Moderators about whether the member is a net positive for the space.

**Ban** – For repeated or severe disregard of the community’s values and guidelines.


Appeals & Feedback
If you believe moderation was unfair or context was missed, you (and others) are encouraged to raise it in <#1136343213091856486>. 
Critiquing mod decisions is allowed — just follow the same respect and good-faith rules as any other discussion.

By being here, you’re helping build a transparent, research-driven, and self-directed investing community.
